    <title>Civilian Aviation Certification Equity Act of 2021</title>
    <titles>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To direct the Administrator of the Federal Aviation Administration to revise regulations to ensure a Department of Defense civilian pilot is eligible for certain ratings in the same manner as a military pilot, and for other purposes.</title>
